@@eThe Saltglass Reach -- As Kowloon Sees It@@N

@@lHarbor Syndics' Maritime Jurisdiction Report@@N

The Saltglass Reach is where inland desert law transforms into
@@ymaritime law@@N, and maritime law is @@lour native tongue@@N. The Harbor
Syndics study this corridor closely because the @@yShoreward Conversion@@N
-- translating cargo obligations from desert charter to maritime risk
law -- is the legal ancestor of our own @@ldock assessment protocols@@N.

The @@WMirror Flats@@N -- hard salt crust from the dead Iseth River --
blind by day and reflect moonlight at night. Caravans cross at dawn
and dusk when reflection is survivable. Our harbor pilots read
Coppersalt Bay's light conditions to time entries through the
@@lTide Gate@@N. Different surface, same discipline of reading light.

The @@rGlasswind Belts@@N are wind-cut silica shards where guides read
glass color to navigate: milky for stable, amber for thermal fault,
@@dviolet for eclipse residue@@N. The Wardens of Iron compare this to
our @@yColors of Power@@N: civic meaning compressed into visual shorthand.
@@eWhen survival depends on speed of reading, color becomes law.@@N

The @@yTariff Cairn Lines@@N -- ruined checkpoint chains -- once served
the same function as our @@lharbor berth assignments@@N: routing cargo
by type, value, and risk. Three parallel routes for light cargo, bulk
goods, and funerary consignments. The Harbor Syndics recognize the
architecture. We run the same triage at every Coppersalt dock.

At the coast stands @@yMafdet@@N. The @@WShoreward Seal@@N -- the legal
threshold between jurisdictions -- is a boundary stone our Syndics
recognize as a @@lharbor mark@@N. The @@WShoreward Assessors@@N who bridged
both legal traditions through conversion charts became Mafdet's
modern Saltweight standard. Our @@gJade Magistracy@@N maintains a
corresponding @@yDelta Conversion Desk@@N for highland trade terms.

Mafdet is potential partner and potential rival. Their @@rRed Sand
Outriders@@N -- a debt-leverage consortium preying on distressed
caravans -- operate on principles we find distastefully familiar.
Debt leverage at the point of desperation is @@rnot commerce, it is
piracy by contract@@N. We patrol against this in Coppersalt Bay.

The @@gReach Wardens@@N patrolling cairn lines are the Reach's version
of our @@eCourier Lantern Office@@N relays -- jurisdiction through
presence. The @@dGlasswalk Guides@@N, neutral navigators guiding anyone
who pays, remind us of our own @@ypilot guild@@N.

The Reach is not natural. The salt is the dead river. The glass is
the catastrophe's echo. The cairns are collapsed law. Kowloon
understands. Our terraced stone carries the @@rAshfall's@@N mark in
every flood channel and sluice gate. @@yLandscape is ledger.@@N
